The paper discusses the problem of recommending technical papers to researchers and conference reviewing committee members, which involves information retrieval, data integration, and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.DB (Databases), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
